  "tasbihatDuaAyatKursiNote": "Wanda ya karanta Āyat al-Kursī baje kowane sallah, ba wani abu yana tsakanin shi da jannati ba sai mutuwa. Imam al-Bāqir (a) ya ce ita ce daya daga manyan ayyukan Qur'ani.",
